Text.Value: Who else was here?
What did he want with these people?
Leave.
West door... took most beautiful people away... never saw again...
Where did your host go?
Information... asked so many questions...
Who killed you?
Work... Counting House... who controls what...
What were you doing here?
Politicians... minor nobles... Fist officers... all sorts...
Talking about what?
Power structures in city... weaknesses... who he needed to control...
Enjoying party... drinking... talking...
What was a clerk doing here?
Sterlac... Senior Clerk in Counting House...
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*
Who are you?
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
Wolves... arrived when our host left... slaughtered us...
Wanted names of senior staff... families... any scandals, secrets...
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

Synopsis: SwD with one of the guests in Ballroom in Cazador's Palace.
